ehalf of Frayed Knot, would like to officially propose the following rule changes:<br>
<br>
-------<br>
<br>
Proposal 1: Minimum number of plane-able characters:<br>
<br>
We propose that rule one be rewritten as follows, lowering the minimum to 30 from 40:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> 1) Minimum number of plane-able characters:<br>
<br>
To make a reservation your guild/group/alliance must consist of a minimum of 30 characters of 46+.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
-------<br>
Proposal 2: No Epic guilds<br>
<br>
We propose Rule 5, and its related sub-rules, be removed entirely.  Not only is this rule outdated, it contains a broken link, which makes following it impossible.<br>
<br>
-------<br>
<br>
